channel.title: Is mopar supposed to do this?
channel.description:
When I'm in the game, there is no one there, but that doesn't surprise me, and when I click on something, like a superpot, it says nothing happened, like it does in normal when you use something with something else. And when I try to open a door, or something like that, I can't, and when I try to get to kalphite, there is no way into the tunnel... Can someone tell me why this is.
Oh, and if anyone has a server they'd like me to join, just tell me it. =)
-Thanks
